{"id":6811,"date":"2012-09-21T11:45:43","date_gmt":"2012-09-21T15:45:43","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=6811"},"modified":"2021-11-08T08:38:29","modified_gmt":"2021-11-08T04:38:29","slug":"martyrs-alive-in-jannah","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/21\/martyrs-alive-in-jannah\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Shuhada: Those killed in the way of Allah alive in Paradise"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abdullah ibn Mas&#8217;ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>The souls of martyrs are alive in the bodies of green birds who have their nests in chandeliers hanging from the Throne of the Almighty. They eat the fruits of Paradise from wherever they wish and they nestle among these chandeliers. Once their Lord cast a glance at them and He said: Do you want anything? They said: What more could we desire? We eat the fruit of Paradise from wherever we wish. Their Lord asked them the same question three times. When they saw that they will continue to be asked, they said: O Lord, we wish that You could return our souls to our bodies so that we could be martyred in Your way once again. When Allah saw that they had no needs, He left them to enjoy<\/strong>.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1887<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <em><strong>Sahih<\/strong> <\/em>(authentic) according to Muslim<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e<strong>\u0623\u064e\u0631\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0627\u062d\u064f\u0647\u064f\u0645\u065